data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET. COME SEE THE NEW ROOF. SELLER IS OFFERING $3,000 AS BUYER'S CHOICE CONCESSION. This larger ranch home with bonus is currently available in the gated community of Carolina Lakes.  A split floor plan exists. The main bath is spa-like with dual sinks, a jetted tub and two partially cedar lined closets.  Tucked on a quiet corner lot, it is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the tranquil nature of country living,  Have your morning coffee on the back porch/deck while enjoying the early morning sounds of nature.  Carolina Lakes offers the usual amenities, plus some unique activities including a farmers' market, boating regattas and July 4 is celebrated over several days with multiple fireworks!  There is always something happening in one of Harnett County's premier family oriented neighborhoods.  Proximity to Ft. Liberty, Pinehurst and Raleigh is a plus. Stop in to see this beautiful home today!  Garage items do not convey.
